      • Tower

        public Tower​(int x,
             int y,
             int iX,
             int iY,
             int cost,
             int range,
             int cooldown,
             greenfoot.GreenfootImage[] images)
        Creates a tower.
        Parameters:
        x - the x coordinate of the tower
        y - the y coordinate of the tower
        iX - the x index of the tower in the global grid
        iY - the y index of the tower in the global grid
        cost - the cost to upgrade the tower
        range - the range of the tower
        cooldown - the number of milliseconds after which a tower will complete an action
        images - an array of greenfoot images for each level of the tower
